// ΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇ Responsive Dashboard Grid ΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇΓöÇ
/**
 * Builds responsive layouts for each breakpoint from the master lg layout.
 * - md: shrink each item width slightly
 * - sm & xs: full-width stacked
 */
function buildResponsiveLayouts(lgLayout) {
  if (!lgLayout?.length) return { lg: [], md: [], sm: [], xs: [] };

  // md: clamp x and w to 10 cols
  const mdLayout = lgLayout.map((item) => ({
    ...item,
    x: Math.min(item.x, 8),
    w: Math.min(item.w, 10),
  }));

  // sm: full width, stacked by y order
  const sortedBySm = [...lgLayout].sort((a, b) => a.y - b.y || a.x - b.x);
  let smY = 0;
  const smLayout = sortedBySm.map((item) => {
    const newItem = { ...item, x: 0, w: 6, y: smY, h: item.h };
    smY += item.h;
    return newItem;
  });

  // xs: 2-col
  let xsY = 0;
  const xsLayout = sortedBySm.map((item) => {
    const newItem = { ...item, x: 0, w: 2, y: xsY, h: Math.max(item.h, 3) };
    xsY += newItem.h;
    return newItem;
  });

  return { lg: lgLayout, md: mdLayout, sm: smLayout, xs: xsLayout };
}

function DashboardGrid({ sheet, sheetId, onLayoutChange, filters }) {
  const layouts = useMemo(
    () => buildResponsiveLayouts(sheet.layout),
    // Only rebuild when the lg layout reference changes
    // eslint-disable-next-line react-hooks/exhaustive-deps
    [sheet.layout]
  );

  const handleLayoutChange = useCallback(
    (_currentLayout, allLayouts) => {
      // Persist the lg layout (master)
      const lg = allLayouts.lg ?? _currentLayout;
      onLayoutChange(lg);
    },
    [onLayoutChange]
  );

  return (
    <div className="dashboard-grid-wrap">
      <ResponsiveGridLayout
        className="dashboard-rgl"
        layouts={layouts}
        breakpoints={BREAKPOINTS}
        cols={COLS}
        rowHeight={ROW_HEIGHT}
        margin={MARGIN}
        containerPadding={[0, 0]}
        onLayoutChange={handleLayoutChange}
        draggableHandle=".card-drag-handle"
        resizeHandles={["se"]}
        isDraggable
        isResizable
        isBounded={false}
        preventCollision={false}
        compactType="vertical"
        useCSSTransforms
      >
        {sheet.charts.map((chart) => {
          const lItem      = sheet.layout.find((l) => l.i === chart.id);
          const pixelH     = lItem ? itemPixelHeight(lItem.h) : itemPixelHeight(4);

          return (
            <div
              key={chart.id}
              className="rgl-item"
              data-grid={lItem ?? { x: 0, y: 9999, w: 4, h: 4, minW: 2, minH: 3 }}
            >
              <ChartCard
                chart={chart}
                pixelHeight={pixelH}
                sheetId={sheetId}
                filters={filters}
              />
            </div>
          );
        })}
      </ResponsiveGridLayout>
    </div>
  );
}

